{"tid":1295511,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"尋晚發撚左個痴線夢 瞓醒後懷疑自己係隱性基佬","createTime":"2019-07-08T04:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T13:19:48.000Z","uid":76399,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"90a618c7f4765f3087f456aa06fe1387fc181366","tid":1295511,"uid":76399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:58:56.000Z","msg":"話說尋日病左，返到屋企食左粒藥就上床瞓覺。<br />\n<br />\n個夢嘅內容係我變返做中學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，同一大班同學搭緊飛機。 點知突然機長開咪話有特別表演，叫我地坐定定。<br />\n<br />\n之後就有個靚女姐姐走左出嚟，係咁色誘啲男同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 捉佢地隻手埋個波到，比佢地瘋狂食波餅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。玩到咁上下佢竟然開始除衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，除左衫之後就露條波gap出嚟，直接對埋佢男同學塊面到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。 又過左冇耐個姐姐就開始跳脫衣舞，一除個胸圍果陣露出兩粒pink lin，搞到全場氣氛高漲。<br />\n<br />\n之後佢跳到咁上下就開始除褲，搞到我都好期待睇下佢嘅鮑鮑係咩色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢一除佢果條黑色底褲果陣，全場氣氛去到最高點，佢色情到不得了嘅底褲下面竟然有條大JJ...... 仲粗撚過黑人....... 機長又開咪話表演完畢乜乜乜 之後發過啲咩我都唔記得了，剩係想知發啲咁嘅夢係咪代表我隱性基？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申青頭 睇av 非基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df0ff0d0ebb40034e84baa1c6ce055bdd7f780f","tid":1295511,"uid":50658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:00:47.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"6db324a0172572034afc903960126e160a6f346c","tid":1295511,"uid":76399,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5df0ff0d0ebb40034e84baa1c6ce055bdd7f780f","tid":1295511,"uid":50658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:00:47.000Z","msg":"係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:06:11.000Z","msg":"係咪睇無碼睇得多搞到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62354256eb49d9d7ef6d34983c5d27f57c766bc2","tid":1295511,"uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor